description: Dai Mubai is the second prince of the royal household in the Star Luo Empire. The heir to the throne is by tradition the strongest in the royal famil, so he and his older brother are rivals. Dai Mubai since the birth of Zhu Zhuqing was promised in marriage to her as per agreement of their families. Dai Mubai left home in order to become stronger and never lose to anyone.
name: Dai Mubai
